            <p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1">I think your right but there is still a big loop hole in this issue. I still have to say when you start the game you come to the user agreement where you hit accept or decline. When you hit I agree you are saying you have read and understand the user agreement. saying that I dont like when a player sells character. <br />
1. If you plan on leaving the game just go. say your good bys and go.<br />
2. You only cause player problems when you sell your account to someone. They dont know how to play that account.<br />
3. The idea of the game is to have fun.<br />
4. If someone thinks there time and effort is worth real cash for time THEY put into it on there time than they dont need to be playing games. <br />
5. This is not a place to go and make an account and and sell it to make money and get rich.<br />
6. If you are done just kill you acount delet your characters and or give it all away.<br />
Don't tell me RL jobs can mean the same as this or any other game out there. The time you spend here is of your owen free will not some money make time. <br />
I dont mind if people sell there account/s or not just understand they could be puting it in someones hands that could cause your friends and others in an odd spot. I love my friends and would do any thing for them and will give others a chance but when they are causeing problems they go on ignor. <br />
Enough Rambling on about this weather we like it or not people are going to do it anyways. I just ask you think and get to know who you are selling too for everyones sake.</font></p>
             
